snippet.title: All Mario Sunshine nozzles recreated in Mario 64
snippet.description:
We will also recreate the entire rest of Sunshine later.
For more fangames, subscribe to this channel!
https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1

I also do livestreams!!
https://www.twitch.tv/kazesm64

Shoutouts to Nikki, Marionova and Doopz for providing me with models.

Download:
https://mega.nz/#!3eJhjQoA!OWA5inmJUcnJ4aCrcWczGCZt80LN5LzbwvMQ3ixy7cw

Controls:
Dpad - select nozzle
L - use nozzle
